  <Docs>
    <summary>Represents a color in HarfBuzz's packed BGRA format.</summary>
    <remarks>Colors are stored as a 32-bit unsigned integer with the layout <c>0xBBGGRRAA</c> (blue in the high byte, alpha in the low byte).</remarks>
  </Docs>
